abstract: Michael Putnam takes lead in Humana Challenge with nine-under-par 63; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Putnam made nine birdies in an 11-hole stretch and finished with a nine-under-par 63 to take a one-stroke lead in the Humana Challenge.
snippet: Putnam made nine birdies in an 11-hole stretch and finished with a nine-under-par 63 to take a one-stroke lead in the Humana Challenge.

headline.main: Michael Putnam Shoots a 63 to Lead Humana Challenge
